race.comment: ACTUALITY (10) hit the line strongly first up at Sandown Hillside behind the smart Just Like Gaby, getting within a long neck on the line. She's not an 1000m horse so the rise in trip here will suit much better and she should have improvement to come with Williams on from the inside gate. LEGIO TEN (1) resumes for a new yard. He's trialled well at Tatura and has largely raced in better company than this, fourth in a BM84 when fresh last time in. Rates well. PER SEMPRE (7) is in flying form, beating a handy field at Flemington last time out. Will have to circle a few here but should run well again. ROYAL LASS (9) is coming off a strong win at Benalla last time out when getting a nice run on speed which she sets up to do so here as well. Can measure up. FISSION (2) needs to find best but has claims.
